issue_body:
### What happened?

Text completion for files and directories no longer work when typing `@` after having [context.fileFiltering.customIgnoreFilePaths](https://geminicli.com/docs/reference/configuration/#the-gemini-directory-in-your-project:~:text=context.fileFiltering.customIgnoreFilePaths) setting added to settings.json

<img width="1040" height="842" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/dee92d78-fbf4-40df-bdd2-7c0d84dc33cd" />

Related to https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/16487 ?

### What did you expect to happen?

Path completion to work after typing @

<img width="372" height="248" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/23bc401c-3384-4511-b177-c1654e47e94c" />

(works after removing fileFiltering from setting)

Removing this fixes the issue:
```
 "context": {
     "fileFiltering": {
       "customIgnoreFilePaths": [
         "node_modules/"
```

